metadata.name: Originalgold Pebble #AndyWarhol [2/2]
metadata.description: This is a limited edition Pebble from Meteo Pebble. It is a parody of Andy Warhol's portrait on the surface of a gold stone pebble. There are two versions of Andy Warhol's forehead, emerald and topaz. Only 2 of the emerald version and the topaz version are produced in Meteo Pebble.
